description: This was one single topic among many as part of the May Mixed Topic survey. Test link to view these questions: https://www.edmontoninsightcommunity.ca/R.aspx?a=310&t=1. Open from May 11 - 19, 2015. At the time the survey was launched survey invitations were sent to 2709 Insight Community Members. 832 members completed the survey which represents a completion rate of 31%. A total of 916 respondents completed the survey: 832 Insight Community Members and 84 using the anonymous link which will have no demographic info.
